DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       YYoouubbeeddaa  is  an  OVZ complainer. It can look after VEs resources limits
       and make some actions on _f_a_i_l_c_n_t value  increase.  VEs  to  look  after
       could be explicitly specified.

   AAvvaaiillaabbllee aaccttiioonnss::
                           - print notification (to stdout and/or logfile
                             and/or syslog);

                           - send notification via email;

                           - send notification via jabber;

                           - write complete statistics for exceeded resource
                             into SQL database and/or SQLite and/or into file
                             or pipe as plain SQL requests;

                           - adjust barrier and limit values for exceeded
                             resources.

       YYoouubbeeddaa  written  in  Perl  and basically needs only core Perl modules.
       However for some actions third-party Perl modules could be needed.

